trailingComments.value:
*
 * Inverse of an matrix
 * 
 * @export
 * @param {Array} x
 * @returns {Array}
 * @example 
 * 
 * inv([[1,2],[3,4]])
 * // [[   -2,    1],
 * //  [  1.5, -0.5]]
